cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.FL, cs.PL, cs.DS

Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with a tableau decision procedure for a logic extension.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper discusses optimization techniques for the decision procedure.
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is relevant as the regular inclusion axioms are characterized by finite automata.
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) could be relevant as the paper discusses on-the-fly propagation of (in)consistency.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) could also be relevant as the paper discusses efficiency and caching techniques.
